Ychwanegu llafariaid efo Acen Grom at allweddell "UK extended" yn  Chrome OS drwy ddefnyddio "AltGr" neu "alt gr" fel allweddell segur.
Rhaid pwyso a gollwng "alt gr", ac yna pwyso a gollwng y llafariad perthnasol.

Adding Circumflexed Welsh vowels to the UK extended keyboard layout in Chrome OS  using "AltGr" as a dead key.
Press and release "alt gr" and then press and release the relevant Welsh vowel.
